'''孟買單軌列車'''是[[印度|印度]][[孟買|孟買]]的[[單軌鐵路|單軌鐵路]]系統，也是孟買一項重要的{{link-en|孟買公共交通|public transport in Mumbai|公共交通}}項目，由{{link-en|孟買大都會區發展局|Mumbai Metropolitan Region Development Authority}}（MMRDA）擁有，由總部位於孟買的{{link-en|拿丁集團|Larsen & Toubro}}和馬來西亞基建公司{{link-en|史格米工程|Scomi}}承建。這條鐵路是{{link-en|昆達拉谷鐵路|Kundala Valley Railway}}和{{link-en|伯蒂亞拉邦單軌電車|Patiala State Monorail Trainways}}在1920年代停駛後，印度第一條通車的單軌鐵路<ref>{{cite news|title=Malaysian company says won bid to build India's first monorail|url=http://www.usatoday.com/money/economy/2008-11-10-3787940519_x.htm|accessdate=2012-02-17|newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2008-11-10}}</ref><ref name=times>{{cite news|title=Mumbai monorail to run in two years|publisher=The Times of India|date=2007-09-27|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/articleshow/2413046.cms|accessdate=2009-03-19|archive-date=2010-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101230195051/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/articleshow/2413046.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

單軌列車一期線路於2009年動工，至2014年2月1日通車，連接瓦達拉（Wadala）和商波爾（Chembur）<ref name="ToI inauguration">{{cite news|last=R.Thendral|first=Inian|title=Mumbai monorail|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/Maharashtra-CM-Prithviraj-Chavan-inaugurates-Mumbai-monorail/articleshow/29718494.cms?utm_source=facebook.com&utm_medium=referral|accessdate=2014-02-01|newspaper=Times of India|date=2014-02-01|archive-date=2014-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304141822/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/Maharashtra-CM-Prithviraj-Chavan-inaugurates-Mumbai-monorail/articleshow/29718494.cms?utm_source=facebook.com&utm_medium=referral|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NDTV inauguration">{{cite news|last=Gupta|first=Saurabh|title=Mumbai monorail to be inaugurated on Saturday|url=http://www.ndtv.com/article/cities/mumbai-monorail-to-be-inaugurated-on-saturday-477248|accessdate=2014-01-30|newspaper=NDTV|date=2014-01-30|archive-date=2014-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131061547/http://www.ndtv.com/article/cities/mumbai-monorail-to-be-inaugurated-on-saturday-477248|dead-url=no}}</ref>。二期線路在2019年3月4日通車，連接瓦達拉和雅各圓環（Jacob Circle）。

== 歷史 ==
=== 背景 ===
[[File:Mumbai_monorail_under_construction_in_Chembur1.JPG|thumb]]
孟買大都會區發展局在2005年提出興建單軌鐵路的計劃<ref name="livemint1">{{cite web |url=http://www.livemint.com/Specials/fyCuMeh4OOmTUTy3hWOZfK/Indias-first-monorail-readies-for-takeoff.html |title=India's first monorail readies for take-off |publisher=Livemint |date=2014-01-29 |access-date=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2022-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121183024/https://www.livemint.com/Specials/fyCuMeh4OOmTUTy3hWOZfK/Indias-first-monorail-readies-for-takeoff.html }}</ref>，原因是{{link-en|孟買供電交通公司交通部|BEST Transport division|孟買的巴士}}非常擁擠，在窄路上開得很慢，既加劇交通擠塞，對乘客也沒有好處。局方表示單軌鐵路將服務[[孟買郊區鐵路|郊區鐵路]]和[[孟買地鐵|地鐵]]未覆蓋的區域，為[[通勤|通勤者]]提供有效率、安全、配有冷氣、舒適、廉宜的公共交通服務<ref>{{cite web|title=Mumbai Monorail Project|url=http://mmrda.maharashtra.gov.in/mumbai-monorail-project|publisher=MMRDA|access-date=2014-02-07|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219083318/http://www.mmrda.maharashtra.gov.in/mumbai-monorail-project|archive-date=2014-02-19}}</ref>。

項目於2008年8月18日獲時任{{en-link|馬哈拉施特拉邦首席部長列表|List of chief ministers of Maharashtra|馬哈拉施特拉邦首席部長}}{{link-en|維拉斯拉奧·德希姆克|Vilasrao Deshmukh}}批准。首期路線將連接{{link-en|雅各環|Jacob Circle}}、{{link-en|瓦達拉|Wadala}}、{{link-en|馬呼爾|Mahul}}和{{link-en|商波爾|Chembur}}，接駁原有的郊區鐵路<ref>{{cite news |author=Devraj Dasgupta, TNN, 14 Aug 2008, 06.25 am IST |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Mumbai/Deshmukh_makes_way_for_1st_monorail_project/articleshow/3362895.cms |title=Deshmukh makes way for 1st monorail project |publisher=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2008-08-14 |accessdate=2010-08-25 |archive-date=2016-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123115410/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Mumbai/Deshmukh_makes_way_for_1st_monorail_project/articleshow/3362895.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由{{link-en|拿丁集團|Larsen & Toubro}}和{{link-en|史格米工程|Scomi}}合資籌建的財團在2008年11月11日擊敗[[龐巴迪運輸|龐巴迪運輸]]、{{link-en|信實基建|Reliance Infrastructure|信實能源}}和[[日立製作所|日立]]組成的財團，中標單軌列車的興建工程，合約總值246億[[印度盧比|盧比]]（約5.15億[[美元|美元]]）。按照合約，單軌鐵路通車後，將由上述財團負責經營，至2029年交還政府<ref>{{cite news|author=Johnlee Varghese|title=Mumbai Gets Ready For India's First Monorail [Facts,Timeline,Photos]|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/articles/536586/20140130/mumbai-monorail-first-city-maharashtra-mass-transport.htm|accessdate=2014-02-10|newspaper=International Business Times|date=2014-01-30|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203012325/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/articles/536586/20140130/mumbai-monorail-first-city-maharashtra-mass-transport.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 施工 ===
[[File:Metro,_Traffic,_Birds_(12151012426).jpg|thumb]]
孟買單軌鐵路在2009年1月舉行動工儀式，由馬哈拉施特拉邦首席部長{{en-link|阿肖克·查萬|Ashok Chavan}}主禮。項目分兩期施工，首期路線連接商波爾和瓦達拉，預計可在2010年12月竣工，第二期路線連接瓦達拉和雅各圓環，預計在2011年6月竣工<ref name="scomitakeoff">{{cite news|last=Tembhekar |first=Chittaranjan|url=http://www.scomigroup.com.my/weboffice/files/news/2102009_52436PM_SEB_Bernama_BT_TI_IT_ET_100209.pdf|title=23L people can walk to nearest monorail station|date=2009-02-10|publisher=[[印度時報|The Times of India]]|access-date=2013-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929214220/http://www.scomigroup.com.my/weboffice/files/news/2102009_52436PM_SEB_Bernama_BT_TI_IT_ET_100209.pdf|archive-date=2013-09-29|url-status=dead}}</ref>。第一期工程延誤了10次<ref>{{cite web |last=Shaikh |first=Ateeq |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-dna-special-cheers-you-can-enjoy-monorail-ride-in-mumbai-by-month-end-1955474 |title=dna special: Cheers! You can enjoy monorail ride in Mumbai by month-end |publisher=DNA |date=2014-01-23 |access-date=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2022-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191724/https://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-dna-special-cheers-you-can-enjoy-monorail-ride-in-mumbai-by-month-end-1955474 }}</ref>，原因是孟買大都會區發展局經常改變單軌走線<ref>{{cite news|last=Mishra|first=Anand|url=http://www.asianage.com/mumbai/delay-due-changed-route-405 |title=Delay due to changed route|newspaper=The Asian Age|date=2014-01-29 |access-date=2014-02-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203025534/http://www.asianage.com/mumbai/delay-due-changed-route-405|archivedate=2014-02-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，承建商又未能及時解決徵地糾紛、移除侵佔物，以及從當局和鐵路部門取得施工許可<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/mumbai-monorail-to-be-ready-by-dec-metro-by-march/174429/on | title=Mumbai monorail to be ready by Dec, Metro by March | location=Mumbai | work=Business Standard | date=2012-06-12 | accessdate=2022-04-08 | archive-date=2012-12-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121228092842/http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/mumbai-monorail-to-be-ready-by-dec-metro-by-march/174429/on }}</ref>。

單軌鐵路一段長108米路段在2010年1月26日完成試車<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.oneindia.in/2010/01/26/trialrun-of-monorail-successful-in-mumbai.html |title=Trial run of monorail successful in Mumbai – Oneindia News |publisher=News.oneindia.in |date=2010-01-26 |accessdate=2010-08-25 |archive-date=2014-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202220128/http://news.oneindia.in/2010/01/26/trialrun-of-monorail-successful-in-mumbai.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，長約1公里的瓦達拉車廠－{{en-link|巴克提園單軌站|Bhakti Park monorail station|巴克提園}}段則於2012年2月18日試車<ref name=mumbaimirror>{{cite news |url=http://www.mumbaimirror.com/article/2/2012021920120219020112507f1b5170/Monorail-takes-its-first-ride-around-town.html |title=Monorail takes its first ride around town |newspaper=Mumbai Mirror |date=2012-02-19 |accessdate=2012-03-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191818/https://mumbaimirror.indiatimes.com/mumbai/other/monorail-takes-its-first-ride-around-town/articleshow/16207566.cms |archivedate=2022-01-21 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。孟買大都會區發展局於同年12月展開全線的測試工作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/endtoend-trial-run-of-monorail-conducted/1035115/ |title=End-to-end trial run of monorail conducted |publisher=Indian Express |date=2012-11-23 |accessdate=2012-12-14 |archive-date=2013-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130213011450/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/endtoend-trial-run-of-monorail-conducted/1035115 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年12月底，孟買大都會區發展局宣布他們已向安全認證局（工程）申請對單軌鐵路瓦達拉－商波爾段進行檢查；上述路線通車前，安全認證局需要檢查文件和實地檢查項目<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-12-28/mumbai/45651273_1_fire-safety-measures-mmrda-monorail |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231162848/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-12-28/mumbai/45651273_1_fire-safety-measures-mmrda-monorail |url-status=dead |archive-date=2013-12-31 |title=Monorail goes for final safety test |newspaper=The Times of India |date=2013-12-28 |access-date=2014-02-02}}</ref>。電機系統由電氣總督察負責認證<ref name=mumbaimirror/>，安全審核則由拿丁-史格米財團委託新加坡[[SMRT集團|SMRT集團]]完成<ref name="indianexpress2">{{cite news |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/monorail-just-a-step-away-from-getting-safety-certificate/ |title=Monorail just a step away from getting safety certificate |newspaper=The Indian Express |date=2014-01-14 |access-date=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2022-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122041837/https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/monorail-just-a-step-away-from-getting-safety-certificate/ }}</ref>。翌年1月20日安全認證局發出安全證書後<ref>{{cite news |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/its-all-clear-for-monorail/ |title=It's all clear for monorail |newspaper=The Indian Express |date=2014-01-21 |access-date=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2022-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122041835/https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/its-all-clear-for-monorail/ }}</ref>，孟買大都會區發展局隨即向邦政府提交證書，以取得對方批准單軌鐵路投運的通知。單軌通車前，其營運和維護的安排需要得到首席部長的批准<ref>{{cite web |last=Shaikh |first=Ateeq |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-mumbai-monorail-clears-safety-signal-all-set-to-roll-1954439 |title=Mumbai monorail clears safety signal, all set to roll |publisher=DNA |date=2014-01-21 |access-date=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2022-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220426130231/https://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-mumbai-monorail-clears-safety-signal-all-set-to-roll-1954439 }}</ref>。

=== 通車 ===
馬哈拉施特拉邦首席部長{{link-en|普利特維拉·查萬|Prithviraj Chavan}}於2014年2月1日下午3時47分為孟買單軌鐵路1號線第一班列車揮動出發旗號，隨後與副首席部長等一眾官員登上單軌列車，從瓦達拉車廠到達商波爾站，全程20分鐘<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mumbaimirror.com/mumbai/others/First-mono-runs-crowded-like-the-good-old-local/articleshow/29729191.cms |title=First mono runs crowded like the good old local |newspaper=Mumbai Mirror |date=2014-02-01 |access-date=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2014-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219151517/http://www.mumbaimirror.com/mumbai/others/First-mono-runs-crowded-like-the-good-old-local/articleshow/29729191.cms }}</ref>。一行人之後到商波爾甘地廣場參加正式的通車典禮<ref>{{cite news |title=India’s first Monorail rolls out in city |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/indias-first-monorail-rolls-out-in-city/ |accessdate=2022-04-08 |location=Mumbai |work=The Indian Express |date=2014-02-06 |archive-date=2022-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422065103/https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/indias-first-monorail-rolls-out-in-city/ }}</ref>。翌日一期路線開放載客，服務時間原訂於下午3點結束，但當天單軌鐵路共招待19,678人次<ref name="dnaindia4">{{cite web |last=Shaikh |first=Ateeq |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-mumbai-monorail-19600-have-joyride-on-day-2-1959195 |title=Mumbai monorail: 19,600 have joyride on Day 2 |publisher=DNA |date=2014-02-04 |access-date=2014-02-19 |archive-date=2022-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220426131814/https://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-mumbai-monorail-19600-have-joyride-on-day-2-1959195 }}</ref>，比預期多，因此車站需要在下午2點30分提早關門。列車服務則延續到下午4點30分，讓每一個購票乘客有機會乘坐單軌列車<ref>{{cite news |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/infrastructure/20000-ride-mumbais-monorail-on-day-1/articleshow/29801017.cms?curpg=2 |title=20,000 ride Mumbai's monorail on Day 1 |newspaper=The Economic Times |date=2014-02-03 |access-date=2014-02-19 |archive-date=2022-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408200030/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/infrastructure/20000-ride-mumbais-monorail-on-day-1/articleshow/29801017.cms?curpg=2 }}</ref>。通車後第一個星期（2月2日－8日），單軌列車共開出512班列車，服務136,865人次，營運商售出132,523枚單程票和1,409張智能卡，錄得1,424,810[[印度盧比|盧比]]的票務收入<ref>{{cite news |last=Jog |first=Sanjay |url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/mumbai-monorail-a-hit-136-000-use-it-in-a-week-114021000017_1.html |title=Mumbai monorail a hit, 136,000 use it in a week |location=Mumbai |newspaper=Business Standard |date=2014-02-10 |access-date=2014-02-19 |archive-date=2021-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211006133826/https://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/mumbai-monorail-a-hit-136-000-use-it-in-a-week-114021000017_1.html }}</ref>。通車後第一個月（2月2日－3月1日），單軌列車共服務458,871人次，總收入為4,466,522盧比<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-30-days-45l-commuters-in-monorail-1966313 |title=30 days, 4.5l commuters in monorail |publisher=DNA |date=2014-03-03 |accessdate=2022-04-08 |archive-date=2022-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220428111718/https://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-30-days-45l-commuters-in-monorail-1966313 }}</ref>。

由於沿線地區人煙稠密，拆除違章建築需時，因此原定於2011年6月完工的二期路線（雅各圓環－瓦達拉）歷經多年延誤<ref>{{cite news |title=Mumbai Monorail Phase II opens up to help with your commuting woes |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/travel/destinations/mumbai-monorail-phase-ii-opens-up-to-help-with-your-commuting-woes/as68560293.cms |date=2019-03-25 |accessdate=2022-04-08 |location=Mumbai |work=Times of India Travel |archive-date=2020-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221213220/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/travel/destinations/mumbai-monorail-phase-ii-opens-up-to-help-with-your-commuting-woes/as68560293.cms }}</ref>，最終在2019年3月3日舉行通車典禮，至翌日（3月4日）開放載客<ref>{{cite news |last=Venkatraman |first=Tanushree |title=Mumbai Monorail: A month after phase-2 was opened, only 5 lakh use corridor |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/mumbai-news/mumbai-monorail-a-month-after-phase-2-was-opened-only-5-lakh-use-corridor/story-bsP8sUQi4TqLZi1R71YIKO.html |accessdate=2022-04-08 |location=Mumbai |work=Hindustan Times |date=2019-04-06 |archive-date=2022-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408200024/https://www.hindustantimes.com/mumbai-news/mumbai-monorail-a-month-after-phase-2-was-opened-only-5-lakh-use-corridor/story-bsP8sUQi4TqLZi1R71YIKO.html }}</ref>。

== 營運 ==
=== 車費 ===
單軌列車按距離收費。剛通車時，單軌列車的單程車費由5至11盧比不等<ref name="NDTV inauguration" />。2019年二期路線通車後，單程車費調高到10至40盧比不等<ref>{{cite news|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/railways/entire-19-54-km-mumbai-monorail-network-now-operational/articleshow/68245606.cms?from=mdr|title=Entire 19.54 km Mumbai monorail network now operational|location=Mumbai|work=The Economic Times|date=2019-03-03|accessdate=2022-04-07|archive-date=2022-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220429003653/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/railways/entire-19-54-km-mumbai-monorail-network-now-operational/articleshow/68245606.cms?from=mdr}}</ref>。

=== 噪音 ===
根據孟買大都會區發展局在單軌試車期間進行的研究，單軌列車產生的噪音達65至85分貝，明顯低於市內巴士（95分貝）<ref>{{cite news|last=Nair|first=Binoo|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report_monorail-quieter-than-best-bus-say-officials_1784489|title=Monorail quieter than BEST bus, say officials|location=Mumbai|work=DNA|date=2013-01-02|accessdate=2013-07-16}}</ref>。

=== 車速 ===
單軌列車最高時速為{{convert|80|km|mi}}，平均時速為{{convert|65|km|mi}}<ref name=times />。加上[[停車時間|停車時間]]後，營運時速約為{{convert|31|km|mi}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.accommodationtimes.com/real-estate-news/monorail-integration-with-cr-wr-and-harbour-line/ | title=Monorail integration with CR, WR and Harbour Line |publisher=Accommodation Times |date=2010-11-26 |access-date=2014-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201030800/http://www.accommodationtimes.com/real-estate-news/monorail-integration-with-cr-wr-and-harbour-line/ |archive-date=2010-12-01 }}</ref>。

=== 載客量與班次 ===
四節單軌列車{{link-en|最高負載量|crush load|在滿載時}}最多可接載568名乘客<ref>{{cite news|url=http://in.news.yahoo.com/photos/trial-run-of-mumbai-monorail-photo-2029372469.html|title=trial run of mumbai monorail photo|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707035634/http://in.news.yahoo.com/photos/trial-run-of-mumbai-monorail-photo-2029372469.html|archivedate=2013-07-07|accessdate=2014-02-08}}</ref>，六節列車則可接載852名乘客<ref>{{cite news|last=Kulkarni|first=Dhaval|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/1718446/report-mumbai-monorail-dream-run-ends-before-take-off|title=Mumbai Monorail dream run ends before take-off|location=Mumbai|work=DNA|date=2012-07-23|accessdate=2013-07-16}}</ref>。每一節車廂設有約18個座位，並可容納124名站立乘客，但首、末兩節列車設有駕駛室，載客量比其他車廂少<ref>{{cite news|title=Mumbai's monorail: Key facts you want to know|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/slideshows/infrastructure/mumbais-monorail-key-facts-you-want-to-know/seating-capacity/slideshow/18555107.cms|accessdate=2014-02-08|archive-date=2014-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302063507/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/slideshows/infrastructure/mumbais-monorail-key-facts-you-want-to-know/seating-capacity/slideshow/18555107.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。按照設計，單軌列車班距最短可達3分鐘，營運時間為清晨5時到凌晨12時<ref>{{cite web|title=Mumbai Monorail Project|url=http://www.mmrda.maharashtra.gov.in/mumbai-monorail-project#|publisher=Mumbai Metropolitan Region Development Authority|accessdate=2014-02-09|archive-date=2014-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219083318/http://www.mmrda.maharashtra.gov.in/mumbai-monorail-project|dead-url=no}}</ref>。預計通車初期，單軌列車的{{link-en|每小時單向載客量|passengers per hour per direction}}為7,400人次（2031年將增至8,300人次），日乘客量為12.5萬人次（2031年將增至30萬人次）<ref>{{cite web|title=MUMBAI MONORAIL PROJECT|url=http://202.54.119.40/monorail.htm|publisher=Mumbai Metropolitan Region Development Authority|accessdate=2014-02-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319170253/http://202.54.119.40/monorail.htm|archivedate=2012-03-19}}</ref>。截至2020年1月，單軌實際的日載客量為1萬人次<ref>{{cite news |last=Tiwari |first=Neeraj |title=Mumbai: In 10 months, Monorail sees 10% of expected ridership |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/mumbai-in-10-months-monorail-sees-10-of-expected-ridership-6210555/ |accessdate=2022-04-08 |location=Mumbai |work=The Indian Express |date=2020-01-11 |archive-date=2022-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408200229/https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/mumbai-in-10-months-monorail-sees-10-of-expected-ridership-6210555/ }}</ref>。

2019年第二期路線通車後，單軌列車的營運時間從清晨6時開始，至晚上10時結束<ref>{{cite web|title=6 Monorails defunct, commuters fume over frequency|url=https://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-6-monorails-defunct-commuters-fume-over-frequency-2737399|location=Mumbai|publisher=DNA|date=2019-04-08|accessdate=2022-04-09|archive-date=2022-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121175658/https://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report-6-monorails-defunct-commuters-fume-over-frequency-2737399}}</ref>。截至2021年，單軌列車的班距為20分鐘；2023年新列車投入運作後，班距將可縮短到5分鐘<ref>{{cite news |last1=Mehta |first1=Manthank |title=Mumbai: Monorail frequency to go from 20 minutes to 5 as 10 new trains ordered |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/mumbai-monorail-frequency-to-go-from-20-mins-to-5-as-10-new-trains-ordered/articleshow/86949986.cms |date=2021-10-12 |accessdate=2022-04-08 |location=Mumbai |work=The Times of India |archive-date=2021-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211226110327/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/mumbai-monorail-frequency-to-go-from-20-mins-to-5-as-10-new-trains-ordered/articleshow/86949986.cms }}</ref>。

== 擱置計劃 ==
